Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:16.02,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(238,174)}服务器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:16.02,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(280,192)}日本伺服器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:16.02,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(236,228)}区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:16.02,zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(266,244)}小田原
